Cue Card Topic: Describe Your Favorite Place

Introduction
My favorite place is a park near my home. I often go there in the morning and evening to relax and enjoy nature.

Description of the Place
The park is very clean and full of green trees and colorful flowers. There is a walking track, a small playground, and many benches to sit and rest.

Why I Like This Place
I like this place because it is peaceful and fresh. I can breathe clean air and feel calm there. It helps me reduce stress and improves my mood.

Activities I Do There
I usually go for a walk, listen to music, and sometimes meet my friends. On weekends, I spend more time there reading or exercising.

Conclusion
This park is very special to me because it gives me happiness and relaxation. It is the best place for me to spend my free time.
